PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period of one year during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to the Hon. ROBERT PIDGEON, a Puisne Judge of the Court of Appeal of Quebec, who was required to relocate from the Town of Rimouski to the City of Quebec.
Attachments
precis:
Order prescribing an additional period of one year during which certain
RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to the Hon. ROBERT PIDGEON, a Puisne
Judge of the Court of Appeal of Quebec, who was required to relocate from
the Town of Rimouski to the City of Quebec.
